name: SENSUALITY
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Develop the velvet touch of your skin throughout your life. Be sensuous, loose, free, buoyant and delicious. Luscious velvet flowing timelessness sinking into warm gently eddies of water that melts the muscles, flowing over the skin and softening everything. 
Have you ever taken the time to eat a peach really slowly. I mean really really, really slowly. Looking at it first seeing the colours and the hues mingling with each other on its surface. Then touch the peach, feel its soft downy outer layer on your fingertips, a perfectly ripe peach soft to the touch. Feel the surface on your lips and open your mouth wider letting your teeth sink into the flesh as the sweet nectar slips down your throat. 

Delicious, expansive & sensuous. Slow down and Experience life.

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
